definitions.definition: The capital city of Yukon , Canada .
An unincorporated community in Chester County , Pennsylvania , United States , named after a tavern.
A census-designated place in Dewey County , South Dakota , United States , named after a chieftain.
A local government area in Melbourne , Victoria , Australia , named after the White Horse Inn, a former tavern; in full, the City of Whitehorse .
